casebody.data:
No. 9372. State ex rel. Stolzenbach v. Feltz, Auditor. (Decided April 4, 1905.) Messrs. Wheeler & Bentley, for plaintiff in error. Messrs. Klinger & Secrest, for defendant in error. Davis, C. J., Shauck, Price, Crew, Summers and Spear, JJ., concur.

Mandamus.

Demurrer to petition overruled and peremptory writ of mandamus awarded as prayed in petition.
